Package <Unnamed>

Class Summary
Avoid Avoidance behavior class, which kicks in when an obstacle is detected less than 30cm ahead, third highest priority class.
BlockPoint BlockPoint Object class, which is used to save two angles and the distance to that object.
Capture Capture behavior class, which kicks in when the flag has been found, second highest priority class.
Driver Driver class which extends DifferentialPilot, only class which has access to the two motors
FinalProject Main class for the final project, execution starts from here.
LCDDisplay LCD Display class displays Odometer information and allows the display to run as a separate timed thread.
LightLocalization Light Localization provides a precise positional and angular localization after USLocalization has been used to find the robot's heading
Navigation Navigation class which extends Navigator, which takes care of following a path made of waypoints as well as generating this path.
PoseProvider PoseProvider (odometry) class which extends OdometryPoseProvider.
Search Search behavior class, which takes care of finding the right block, has highest priority.
Team08Robot Team08Robot Class gives access to : All the hardware properties of the robot: sensors, navigation, odometry, etc.
Travel Search behavior class, first behavior in action, has lowest priority.
USLocalization Ultrasonic Localization class.
